42 SECTION 4.(a) G.S. 113A-103 is amended by adding a new subdivision to read:
43 "(8a) "Man-made ditches" mean constructed, altered, or excavated features used to
44 convey water, including, but not limited to, artificial ponds, culverts, canals,
45 swales, storm channels, minor-drainage features, and roadside ditches. For
46 purposes of this subdivision, the term "altered" does not include the alteration
47 of a natural shoreline, and the term "excavated" does not include submerged
48 lands that have been dredged for the purpose of navigation."
